{"tid":1388451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［再post多一次］遊擊戰重點係hit and run  冇hit 嘅 be water 喺冇打擊力","createTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:46:20.000Z","uid":233118,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ba90d8559832bfa5e192fc5ef79f2d3b3915419e","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"首先有請葵涌嘅巴打示範<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCvjcd0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCvjcd0.gif&h=c5125a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係小型衝突中嘅hit-and-run<br />\n<br />\n擴大層面去到中層（街巷）<br />\n<br />\n攻破警方防線打到佢哋碌柒+解除武裝搶裝備，喺其他警犬過嚟支援之前，轉去第二個街口再打過<br />\n<br />\n再擴大層面去到整個活動<br />\n<br />\n勇武完成目的，e.g. 攻入中聯辦<br />\n然後大家一齊散水<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解惑區</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好畀自己部署嘅防線限制咗自己， 死守喺防線面前<span style=\"color: red;\">唔做任何嘢只不過係做肉盾做靶</span><br />\n<br />\n而家警察已經陷入瘋狂狀態，係唔係都射催淚彈開槍，死守嘅話重傷嘅一定係我哋，一就<span style=\"color: red;\">撤退轉換防線</span>，一就<span style=\"color: red;\">衝鋒</span>，咁樣先至可以最大程度保護我哋<br />\n<br />\n警犬近夜晚先開始清場，一來係未部署好，二來係夜晚環境形勢對佢哋有利，所以行動必須要越早越好，越夜越危險，<span style=\"color: gold;\">前線想要做嘢唔該襯早，唔好猶豫不決咁拖到夜晚</span><br />\n<br />\n前線聚集嘅人數一定會多個警犬防線，理論上大規模衝鋒警犬係擋唔住，問題係前線猶豫不決嘅心態，好容易喺對方一輪推進之後嚇到後退，陷入輪迴，<span style=\"color: gold;\">麻煩你哋堅定自己嘅決心</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">最簡單係催眠自己：我要保護各位兄弟姊妹，如果有人衝鋒我就要去保護佢，至少要打低一個</span><br />\n<br />\n速龍永遠喺防暴推進之後，民眾後退嘅時候做執雞狗，喺後面拉住後退嘅群眾，再撳佢喺地下，<span style=\"color: red;\">但係其實速龍數量唔多</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔需要害怕速龍，要記住佢哋係一個打十個</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大規模後退嘅時候唔可以背脊朝著警犬</span>，警犬最鍾意喺背後拉人落地， 你一定要好似野外見到野狗一樣啤住佢，寧願慢慢後退都唔好畀機會佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要保護手足，比人捉住就一齊反擊，心裏面要不斷催眠自己：我哋要一齊走，我唔揼低任何一個人，有人畀狗捉我就要幫手打，然後帶佢走</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該睇到呢篇文章之後喺心裏面默念3次上面嘅自我催眠，然後再加多句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: orange;\">我要反擊，我要製止黑警，我要守護香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前文<br />\n［戰略導向］［由 準。勇武邁向 真。勇武］遊擊戰將由be water 升級至hit and run<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1bcfa02da3292e6a2de85cac24c8556348e7f06","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3be384bfbe849a26e3963fb6800a2fcdcce7ae52","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:51.000Z","msg":"反擊啦"},{"pid":"839889f6969bb806cfbc645325e76026dd7fb8ad","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"唔好再做靶，一就反擊，一就轉陣地"},{"pid":"4a859710996605d5ffe7953a000fe1388e5e2a38","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"另外提多句轉陣地呢個concept好重要<br />\n遲啲會出水砲車<br />\n所以一定要好清晰，唔好固執死守"},{"pid":"fcb340ca4eb092d7403ddc2de7b0c1794be297f4","tid":1388451,"uid":130585,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7XtP8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7XtP8L.png&h=63472a15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edfc8e61f15874fbcb2fe29b966eefd7b66e9810","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:57:32.000Z","msg":"唔想再有人畀人捉就互相保護大家<br />\n反擊先至可以救到兄弟"},{"pid":"5d3bff6316e7d7c6a86704de57b1934a29c1367c","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港唔係口號<br />\n勇武制暴先係王道"},{"pid":"17f37dc025d52ea8d6e5c4819ff1fa31a14fd29e","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"有人畀人㩒喺地下唔該你上前打走啲警犬，扶佢起身，然後再後退"},{"pid":"d063323a7a36b5fc5087d2d52f9537bcf5a433dd","tid":1388451,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"我諗起整蠱專家某個橋段有個光頭佬成日俾周星馳亨個頭"},{"pid":"06c7c865bf2f013384f296d9200d518e3156401d","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"走之前往清楚有冇兄弟畀人捉住<br />\n有嘅就搵架撐打返警犬轉頭<br />\n然後帶住兄弟走"},{"pid":"63db87142701205fa73545ec0fe0b85ad5bae05d","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"push la"},{"pid":"d19dc9ab81421a0cdf7de84eb4f8cc3f7c612135","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅千祈唔好再死守喺自己條防線<br />\n防線可以再整<br />\n人受傷咗係切實打擊"},{"pid":"166ad8314277d7f3df0cfd1c847331fe151f10d8","tid":1388451,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"有頭盔打頭冇用 除非你鐵棍<br />\n打身掃腳重好"},{"pid":"712136b6305de226c129f49e7a524b41f2cdae11","tid":1388451,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"復仇反擊戰<br />\n正式開波!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9901b2f2fa01dd7f36b4c54188126e61bbd5791","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:02:13.000Z","msg":"你話令到啲狗ot<br />\n令到佢哋精神崩潰<br />\n我冇所謂<br />\n但係我比較prefer更有效率嘅做法<br />\n<br />\n打低佢哋，搶gear然後be water"},{"pid":"d69d011e87d8e31f4507501f6057adfa1e7e25ed","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"大家有勇氣，有裝備<br />\n但係就係缺乏咗一個目的<br />\n<br />\n如果你企喺條防線面前猶豫不決，不如撤退<br />\n<br />\n但如果你清晰知道目標係乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">just do it</span>"},{"pid":"018b64db8928e16a7d1453d09c82eecfa7168a44","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"每一次喺前線或者電視上面見到嘅就係<br />\n<br />\n一堆人死守喺防線面前<br />\n防暴一衝擊<br />\n前面一批人反抗<br />\n後面一批人準備走<br />\n<br />\n結果就係反抗嘅人見到唔對路又後退去第2條防線，畀人撳住打<br />\n<br />\n另一種情況就係軍心散渙，防暴一衝鋒全部人背住佢哋向後擠擁，結果畀速龍逐個擊破<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該你哋我哋真係要反擊啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd99c6f42654f381b09cd1699e6c79d2976ea0a1","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:07:57.000Z","msg":"幫手推好冇<br />\n畀前線睇到"},{"pid":"7da6982a8975f83b61275c9d7c2da29ba158ac2c","tid":1388451,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"下次試吓講 「我而家走」「我幾點會走」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtpNmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtpNmS</a>"},{"pid":"8de9db18c82694f4dd08b04aaa4cb2084c646734","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"hit and run la"},{"pid":"b3926f8155d5a86642e5a89a8bfb723aabff5a8d","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"唔對路嘅就run咗去第二度再hit"},{"pid":"13537e6c905f69ebf3f00d11db98525f84c6a33a","tid":1388451,"uid":16706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42c043ecbd6e9f216a2fa0ebc023b29e1d4cf158","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"流程<br />\nassemble&gt;hit&gt;run&gt;assemble&gt;hit&gt;run<br />\n<br />\nassemble&gt;發現唔對路&gt;run&gt;assemble&gt;hit"},{"pid":"5fdb07751dfb5edb5315625ba415ca40a0b7208f","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c043ecbd6e9f216a2fa0ebc023b29e1d4cf158","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"流程<br />\nassemble&gt;hit&gt;run&gt;assemble&gt;hit&gt;run<br />\n<br />\nassemble&gt;發現唔對路&gt;run&gt;assemble&gt;hit"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"push&gt;push&gt;push&gt; hit and run"},{"pid":"41d1e5aa0c66a1f248eea219d7d5d69f34c6011f","tid":1388451,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"4261eb1bb21c9a2da6f5f6aed319cf1e544164da","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"前線重甲做擋<br />\n輕甲做突擊<br />\n再加弓箭手"},{"pid":"9f27cbd6514c6c17bdc2d57123fea4286c7686b5","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n三罷都唔好忘記武裝自己思想"},{"pid":"e2cf83af1531638e49c9071c658a4f56afd18437","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329f750374f17855a192f76703a6663e86396dcc","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"唔可以再有前線白白送頭"},{"pid":"fe0a5ddb0c860ac4a8743b5dc79879574b9e9609","tid":1388451,"uid":268342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:19:04.000Z","msg":"選擇目標，放棄難度大危險高的目標eg：水炮車，去選低成本易成功的，eg車，好多人都有車，我又有車，你又有車，官都有車.....圍就圍小人既，人多蝦人少，我發夢嗰時諗到。"},{"pid":"b4b2221c5cfb345c4166644716a9c523ebad7e5b","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b97bc890e145059d90522e6318207f29d5de801","tid":1388451,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"爭取民意、國際支持，唔好進攻、還擊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386532</a>"},{"pid":"45422a4746e15b114cde8cb2394e2b28409156a3","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b97bc890e145059d90522e6318207f29d5de801","tid":1388451,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"爭取民意、國際支持，唔好進攻、還擊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386532</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"248284935b8d9e90362c3fa3cefdbca514ba34d7","tid":1388451,"uid":90515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"聚集一班人，設路障，噴黑交通燈，去隔離街，再設路障，再噴黑交通燈，見到黑警，散水去其他區，設路障，噴黑交通燈，重復重復再重復<br />\n<br />\n原因: 以不被捕不受傷為大前題，同狗方硬碰硬係無勝算，裝備訓練各方面都輸曬。不過黑警弱點好明顯。裝備厚重、部署時期長，耐力低。每次出動至少幾個鐘，相當於一個跑唔郁嘅大隻佬。所以死守一個地方幾個鐘係無用，要以速度對抗力量<br />\n<br />\nQ. 啲狗一黎，無人守嘅路障立即被秒殺，有撚用？<br />\n<br />\nA. 路障可以即刻拆，但噴黑左嘅交通燈無得即刻處理。而且透過不停制作路障，大大增加狗方需要嘅覆蓋範圍，等於迫班防暴速龍係咁跑<br />\n<br />\n結語: 避其鋒，攻其短，絕不能再犧牲勇武派！<br />\n<br />\n利申：FF"},{"pid":"4f7c429872e1017d81ccffc5512f8ef830ae1e1f","tid":1388451,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"冇hit嘅 be water係散水only"},{"pid":"17bea06138ed85ba74b3a84034e1ccb77425c6c8","tid":1388451,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"248284935b8d9e90362c3fa3cefdbca514ba34d7","tid":1388451,"uid":90515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"聚集一班人，設路障，噴黑交通燈，去隔離街，再設路障，再噴黑交通燈，見到黑警，散水去其他區，設路障，噴黑交通燈，重復重復再重復<br />\n<br />\n原因: 以不被捕不受傷為大前題，同狗方硬碰硬係無勝算，裝備訓練各方面都輸曬。不過黑警弱點好明顯。裝備厚重、部署時期長，耐力低。每次出動至少幾個鐘，相當於一個跑唔郁嘅大隻佬。所以死守一個地方幾個鐘係無用，要以速度對抗力量<br />\n<br />\nQ. 啲狗一黎，無人守嘅路障立即被秒殺，有撚用？<br />\n<br />\nA. 路障可以即刻拆，但噴黑左嘅交通燈無得即刻處理。而且透過不停制作路障，大大增加狗方需要嘅覆蓋範圍，等於迫班防暴速龍係咁跑<br />\n<br />\n結語: 避其鋒，攻其短，絕不能再犧牲勇武派！<br />\n<br />\n利申：FF"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"呢個係其中一個方法<br />\n<br />\n但係有陣時發現如果對方佈防好少<br />\n例如得50隻狗要我哋有千幾人<br />\n可以嘗試下先發制人<br />\n<br />\n重點係畀人圍捕嘅時候一定要反擊<br />\n唔係落單嘅兄弟會有好大危險"},{"pid":"21db4eb212c844648ec0f0232aa5b2b1b871c0e4","tid":1388451,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislik